### 1. LOGIN - Get JWT (Admin)
POST http://localhost:3000/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "adminpassword"
}

### 2. RETAILER LISTING (SR only) - Paginated + Search + Filters
GET http://localhost:3000/retailers?page=1&limit=10&search=dhaka&regionId=1&areaId=2
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt_rep}}

### 3. RETAILER DETAIL (SR only)
GET http://localhost:3000/retailers/RET-001
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt_rep}}

### 4. UPDATE RETAILER (SR only) - allowed fields
PATCH http://localhost:3000/retailers/RET-001
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt_rep}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "points": 150,
  "routes": "Route A > B > C",
  "notes": "High potential customer"
}

### 5. ADMIN: List Regions
GET http://localhost:3000/admin/regions
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt_admin}}

### 6. ADMIN: Create Region
POST http://localhost:3000/admin/regions
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt_admin}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Sylhet"
}

### 7. ADMIN: Update Region
PATCH http://localhost:3000/admin/regions/1
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt_admin}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Dhaka Metro"
}

### 8. ADMIN: Delete Region
DELETE http://localhost:3000/admin/regions/1
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt_admin}}

### 9. ADMIN: Bulk Import Retailers (CSV)
POST http://localhost:3000/admin/retailers/import
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt_admin}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW

------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="retailers.csv"
Content-Type: text/csv

< ./sample-retailers.csv
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW--

### 10. ADMIN: Bulk Assign Retailers to SR
POST http://localhost:3000/admin/assignments/bulk
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt_admin}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "salesRepId": 2,
  "retailerIds": [1, 2, 3, 4, 5]
}

### 11. ADMIN: Bulk Unassign Retailers
POST http://localhost:3000/admin/assignments/unassign
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt_admin}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "salesRepId": 2,
  "retailerIds": [3, 4]
}